<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>174</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw nuoi simlei tuol I lennau,
 Ngaihte tawh kikhenna;
 $ Aw, bangtik leh ka pawtsan dem?
 Albang vaihna gam hi. (2)

[V2]
 2. Si-al sawm leng vaigei in bawn,
 Thangvan lailung a bel
 $ Aw kei hi la nuoi simlei ah,
 Albang ka vai zing hi. (2)

[V3]
 3. Mi gen lungsietna vak nuomah,
 Liengvaite chawlhna mun;
 $ Aw, ka lautha, sieng va lawiin,
 Albang vai ta lo di'n. (2)

[V4]
 4. Nuoi simlei a gieklawiva bang,
 Liengvai in um mahleng;
 $ Pielgal sau lun a ka len tieng,
 Albang vai ta puo'ng ie. (2)</lyrics>
<title>Albang Vai Ta Puong ie</title>
</song>